data.description: Are you looking for a home that offers the perfect combination of comfort and amazing views? Look no further than this spacious home in Hermantown! As you step into this beautiful property, you're immediately greeted by a warm and cozy atmosphere that welcomes you home. The property features an open and semi updated kitchen and dining area that's perfect for entertaining guests or having a family meal. The living room, with its great natural lighting, is a perfect spot for relaxation after a long day. The main level boasts two spacious bedrooms and a full bath. The upper level is home to a massive master bedroom, with a private sitting room, balcony deck with screened porch, private master bath, walk-in closet, and laundry room. On the lower level, you'll find a rec room, bedroom, 3/4 bath, workshop/utility room. If you're someone who enjoys the outdoors, you'll love the backyard at this property. The large deck, complete with a pool and hot tub, provides a stunning view of the backyard. The mature apple trees, Tonka and Waneta plum trees, and blueberry bushes add a touch of nature to the property. And with plenty of room for outdoor activities, you'll never run out of things to do. As if the property features mentioned above weren't enough, this property also includes an attached 2+ stall garage and a bonus 4-car garage and a second driveway. This provides ample space for all your vehicles, toys and ensures that you never have to worry about parking or storage. Call today for more information or to schedule a visit to this amazing property.
